msgid ""
"Kollision is a casual game where you need to throw your ball and avoid the "
"others balls on the table as long as possible."
msgstr ""
"Kollision pilota joko informal bat da, non zure pilota jaurti eta besteenak "
"ahal duzun luzeen saihestu behar dituzun."
